    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy 12 games in one with the perfect reproduction of real pinball machines, with all kinds of graphic details and sounds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover all the secrets, in these thrilling games, a great challenge awaits you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete all the missions and become number 1 in the world or the best among your Friends, posting your high score on the online leaderboard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Arcade design.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- More than 8 missions to accomplish for game! Are you ready?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Multiball, Extraball, Skillshot, Jackpots...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Reproduction with all the details, lights and sounds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 4 different cameras to choose from.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Vertical Gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Online Leaderboards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you prefer, you can also purchase them separately in the Steam Store.</p>",
